formThreeBId.notesToCertificate:
1.	We have given the certificate on the basis of books of accounts certified by the partners of the partnership firm
2.	The Carpet area and sale amount of unit amount of the project are given after certified by the promoter of the projects.
3.	The Detail of project loan is given after certified by the promoter. The Promoter has repaid all the secured loan taken from the bank
4.	The Details of the customer and NOC and Date of Registration of Agreement for sale is given after certified by the promoter of the project.
5.	The Estimated amount mentioned in the certificate is given after certified by the partner of the firm 
6.	The Promoter has taken additional Loan which is allowed during the COVID-19 by the government hence combined data / amount given by the us at the time of giving certificate.
7.	In some cases, the promoter on request of the customer directly registered sale deed without entering the agreement for sale with the allotees, in this case, we have mentioned the registration of sale deed in that cell while giving the certificate
